CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: QCR Holdings Inc is a multi-bank holding company. The bank operates through segments namely Commercial Banking, Wealth Management, and all other segments. The commercial bank segment is geographically divided by markets namely QCBT, CRBT, CSB and SFCB. It generates revenue in the form of interest.
